<html>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #333;">
  <h2 style="color: #228B22;">✓ Exchange Server Maintenance Completed Successfully</h2>
  
  <table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 20px 0;">
    <tr style="background-color: #f0f0f0;">
      <td style="padding: 8px; font-weight: bold; width: 30%;">Environment:</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px;">{{ environment_type | upper }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; font-weight: bold;">Database:</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px;">{{ target_database }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr style="background-color: #f0f0f0;">
      <td style="padding: 8px; font-weight: bold;">Completion Time:</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px;">{{ completion_time | default(ansible_date_time.iso8601) }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; font-weight: bold;">Job ID:</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px;">{{ tower_job_id | default('N/A') }}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <h3 style="color: #0066cc;">Maintenance Summary:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Database maintenance mode: <strong>EXITED</strong></li>
    <li>Exchange services: <strong>VERIFIED</strong></li>
    <li>Mail flow: <strong>RESTORED</strong></li>
    <li>Server health: <strong>NORMAL</strong></li>
  </ul>

  {% if maintenance_reason is defined %}
  <h3 style="color: #0066cc;">Maintenance Reason:</h3>
  <p>{{ maintenance_reason }}</p>
  {% endif %}

  <h3 style="color: #0066cc;">Performed Actions:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Preparation and environment checks completed</li>
    <li>Active database moved (if applicable)</li>
    <li>Maintenance mode activated and exited</li>
    <li>Queue monitoring and export completed</li>
    <li>Exchange services verified and running</li>
    <li>Alert monitoring restored</li>
  </ul>

  <div style="background-color: #f0f0f0; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #228B22;">
    <strong>Status:</strong> All maintenance tasks completed successfully. The Exchange server is operating normally.
  </div>

  {% if change_request_number is defined and change_request_number %}
  <p><strong>Change Request:</strong> {{ change_request_number }}</p>
  {% endif %}

  <hr style="margin: 20px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ccc;">
  <p style="font-size: 11px; color: #666;">
    This is an automated notification from the STAMP Exchange Maintenance Automation system.<br>
    For support, contact: {{ notifications.default_contacts | join(', ') }}
  </p>
</body>
</html>
